article.description: Zach Moer scored a career-high 16 points and grabbed eight rebounds, Zach Kocur added 14 points and Air Force beat NAIA-member Johnson & Wales 80-56 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Zach Moer, Air Force beat Johnson & Wales 80-56
article.linkText: Zach Moer, Air Force beat Johnson & Wales 80-56
article.story: COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo. -- Zach Moer scored a career-high 16 points and grabbed eight rebounds, Zach Kocur added 14 points and Air Force beat NAIA-member Johnson & Wales 80-56 on Tuesday night. Frank Toohey added a career-high 10 points for Air Force (8-4), which outrebounded JWU 42-33 and forced 18 turnovers. The Falcons scored the first seven points of the game and never trailed. They closed the first half on a 9-2 run for a 38-29 lead as Johnson & Wales went without a field goal for over six minutes. Air Force opened the second half with a 10-2 run for a 17-point lead and Johnson & Wales did not get closer than 11 points the rest of the way. Aaron Stone scored 14 points for Johnson & Wales, which was limited to 17-of-55 shooting (30.9 percent).
